channel.title: I need Port-Forwarding help!
channel.description:
Hello,
Ive recently have created a moparscape server of my own. But theres 1 little problem. I have wireless internet for my laptop. I follow portforwarding.com but people still cant connect. And im a little confused about how the static ips help. Idk which ones to choose.
Help please!
Thanks.
